cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with human pose estimation from images, which is a common problem in computer vision. The proposed method uses texture consistency as a form of supervision, which is a novel approach. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with 3D human body models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of deep learning and the proposed loss function suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
